1. Install the  Node.js from https://nodejs.org/en/download/
2. Run CMD , npm install -g create-react-app 
3. create-react-app my-app // name is always be low case.
4. Start Visual Code, open the fold my-app created as above.
     Remember install Beautify and Simple React Snippets extensions in VS Code.

5. start the web server: 
    cd my-app
    npm start


6. Use Chrome open http://localhost:3000/
    Remember install the React Developer tool from Chrome Web Store
